OL,4,CJudge orders Muslim woman to remove
OL,5,Cveil during High Court dispute
OL,6, A judge ordered a Muslim woman to
OL,7, remove her veil while giving evidence
OL,8, at a virtual High Court hearing.
OL,10,FThe woman was embroiled in a dispute
OL,11,Fwith her estranged husband over their
OL,12,Fchildren.
OL,14,FShe did not wish to be seen "unveiled"
OL,15,Fby male participants unless the judge
OL,16,Fdeemed it "necessary", barrister
OL,17,FAlistair Perkins said.
OL,19,FJudge Sarah Morgan said she should
OL,20,Funcover her face when she and her
OL,21,Festranged husband were giving evidence.
